d
D=\{(t_1,\cdots,t_d)\, |\, 0<t_1\leq t_2\leq \cdots \leq t_d<1  \}
\Delta^{d} = \{  (x_1, \dots, x_{d+1}) \in \mathbb R^{d+1} \;|\; \sum_{k=1}^{d+1} x_k = 1 \text{ and } 0 \leq x_1, \dots, x_{d+1} \leq 1 \}
d
t_i := \sum_{k=1}^{i} x_k
1 \leq i \leq d+1
0 \leq t_1 \leq \dots \leq t_d \leq t_{d+1} = 1
x_1=0
x_{d+1} = 0
